  "texts": [
    "The softmax function 𝜎 is used to calculate the attention weights for the small windows.",
    "Training and TestingThe training process of FCVAE incorporates three key technologies: CVAE-based modified evidence lower bound (CM-ELBO), missing data injection, as well as the newly proposed masking the last point.",
    "As shown in (6), CM-ELBO is obtained by applying M-ELBO [50] to CVAE.",
    "Missing data injection [30,50] is a commonly used technique in VAE that we directly apply.",
    "We observed that an anomalous point in time series data manifests as an outlier value in the time domain."
  ]
}